name: Five nights at Gianluca
description:
It is FNAF fangame.

My first game ever I Have worked on it very hard I hope you like it!

Still in development The Full version will be avaible soon!

Since this is just an Alpha there are some cheats. 

If you press 9 you can skip an hour

if you press 8 you can bring power to 5%

down and up arrow keys to change nights(it will probably be included in the full version)
